#: ../docs/en/cryptography/asymmetric/public-key.md:40
#, no-wrap
msgid "Use cases"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: ../docs/en/cryptography/asymmetric/public-key.md:43
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"[Monero address](/public-address/standard-address) is composed of public spend key and public view key.\n"
"These keys are used to build stealth addresses to receive payments.  \n"
msgstr ""
